MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2002-Cab. (i)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 26th August, 2002
4 Bhadrapada, 1924 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from the 26th August,
2002 : -
i)
The Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Power;
ii)
Shri Anant Gangaram Geete relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State in the Ministry of Finance and Company Affairs and
assumed the charge of the office of Minister of Power;
iii)
Shri L.K. Advani, Deputy Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the
office of Minister of Coal and Mines. He will continue to hold the charge of
the office of Minister of Home Affairs;
iv)
Sushree Uma Bharti relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Youth Affairs and Sports and assumed the charge of the office of Minister
of Coal and Mines;
Shri Vikram Verma assumed the charge of the office of Minister of Youth
Affairs and Sports;
v)
Shri Anandrao Vithoba Adsul assumed the charge of the office of Minister
of State in the Ministry of Finance and Company Affairs.
vi)
